<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٥ و ٦ - <span class="c2">(وَجُنُونٍ وَإِغْمَاءٍ لَا احْتِلَامَ فِيهِمَا)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٧ - <span class="c2">(وَاسْتِحَاضَةٍ)</span>، فَيُسَنُّ لِلْمُسْتَحَاضَةِ أَنْ تَغْتَسِلَ <span class="c2">(لِكُلِّ صَلَاةٍ)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
