<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١٠ - <span class="c2">(وَ)</span> لِدُخُولِ <span class="c2">(حَرَمِهَا)</span> أَيْ مَكَّةَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
